day.description:
The most powerful lies are the ones we want to believe. 
Yet the heart beats only for what is real;
waiting to remind us we know better.

night.description:
The most vital things in life often defy explanation.
Wisdom begins where certainty ends;
Embrace the adventure of the unknown.

night.ritual:
Search out your heartbeat;
in your wrist, your chest, your neck. 
Invite its pulse to become the lullaby that helps you drift off.
